data.description: Fantastic one-story Sommerville plan on a large Corner lot! This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath home has a 2 car garage, high ceilings tons of natural light, large windows and full of upgrades including: granite counters, vinyl plank floors, large garden tub & separate shower! Spacious open kitchen has a huge island with granite countertops, a breakfast bar and is a great space for entertaining and cooking. Kitchen has high quality gorgeous high quality 42' white cabinets, granite counters & gas range. Spacious primary bedroom w/a huge walk-in closet! Oversized backyard is perfect for entertaining w/an outdoor covered tent that stays! Home features a covered back & front patio, garage door opener & ALL APPLIANCES INCLUDED! Close to area shopping & Highways. AVAILABLE NOW!!!
